      <header>Good People of Amadicia!</header>
      <slot>5</slot>
      <level>199</level>
      <author>377461</author>
      <date>1057011866</date>
      <authorname>Garn</authorname>
      <text>*A sheet of thick parchment is pinned to the board by a heavy-bladed dagger*

Citizens of Amador!
    Keep hope!  Though these slaves of the Shadow have triumphed for now,
fear not!  They shall not walk the streets of our city without fear, for
even now those who Serve the Light gather to send them back across the
sea, where they belong!  Do not fear the masters of the shadow-spawned
beasts that terrorize you, or the evil witches who now walk your streets
unashamed, for they will be thrown down!  Down with the Invading Scum!
Down with the Seanchan Tyrants!  For the Children and Amadicia!
</text>
